                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-500/90">Parcial 1</h3>
                <span class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 text-green-400/70 font-mono text-xs">
